lead_paragraph: A.J. Hammons scored 17 points and had four blocks while Rapheal Davis added 16 points Thursday to lead No. 20 Purdue past Michigan 87-70.

headline.print_headline: No. 20 Purdue Dominates Middle in 87-70 Win Over Michigan
